## 2. Surfaces, Cards, and Borders

### 2.1 Prefer Borders Over Shadows (Especially on iOS)

**Rule**: Luxury UIs are quiet. Use hairline borders. Subtle elevation only for modals/floating elements.

**Design Guidance**:
- **Prefer thin lines** — use `StyleSheet.hairlineWidth` or `1px` borders
- **Subtle shadows** — only for modals and floating elements
- **Negative space** — use whitespace instead of heavy visual elements
- **Avoid gradients in light mode** — flat tones feel more premium
- **Avoid glow effects** — rely on contrast and spacing instead

**Border Implementation**:
```typescript
// ✅ GOOD: Hairline border (thin line)
<View style={{
  borderWidth: StyleSheet.hairlineWidth,
  borderColor: theme.border.default,
  borderRadius: BORDER_RADIUS.lg,
}}>

// ✅ GOOD: Subtle shadow only for modals (not cards)
<Modal style={{
  shadowColor: '#000',
  shadowOffset: { width: 0, height: 2 },
  shadowOpacity: 0.1,  // Subtle, not heavy
  shadowRadius: 8,
  elevation: 4, // Android
}}>

// ❌ BAD: Heavy shadows everywhere
<View style={{
  shadowOpacity: 0.3,  // Too heavy
}}>

// ❌ BAD: Gradients in light mode
<View style={{
  background: 'linear-gradient(...)', // No gradients!
}}>
```

---

### 2.2 Border Radius: Consistent and Moderate

**Rule**: Pick one radius scale and stick to it.

**Recommended Radius Scale**:
```typescript
export const BORDER_RADIUS = {
  none: 0,
  sm: 10,   // Small controls (10-12 range)
  md: 14,   // Cards (14-16 range)
  lg: 18,   // Sheets/Modals (18-24 range)
} as const;
```

**Usage**:
- **Small controls** (buttons, inputs): `BORDER_RADIUS.sm` (10-12)
- **Cards**: `BORDER_RADIUS.md` (14-16)
- **Sheets/Modals**: `BORDER_RADIUS.lg` (18-24)

**❌ FORBIDDEN**: 
- Tiny radii (looks "default")
- Excessive rounding (looks playful)
- Inconsistent radius values

---

### 2.3 Card Structure Rule

**Rule**: A card must have clear structure: header (title + optional action), content area, optional footer.

**Card Template**:
```typescript
<View style={styles.card}>
  {/* Header */}
  <View style={styles.cardHeader}>
    <Text style={TEXT_STYLES.h2}>{title}</Text>
    {action && (
      <TouchableOpacity onPress={action.onPress}>
        <Text>{action.label}</Text>
      </TouchableOpacity>
    )}
  </View>
  
  {/* Content */}
  <View style={styles.cardContent}>
    {children}
  </View>
  
  {/* Optional Footer */}
  {footer && (
    <View style={styles.cardFooter}>
      {footer}
    </View>
  )}
</View>
```

**❌ FORBIDDEN**: "Floating random content" without structure.

